org.blockchain_innovation.factom.client.api.rpc

Enum RpcMethod

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<RpcMethod>
      • org.blockchain_innovation.factom.client.api.rpc.RpcMethod
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<RpcMethod>

    public enum RpcMethod
extends java.lang.Enum<RpcMethod>
    This represents all RpcMethods accepted by factomd and walletd. Please note that the enum names used here sometimes differ slightly from the official names (used as argument). This is because the factomd and walletd APIs aren't fully consistent. Entry Credits are for instance referenced as ec, entry-credit, entrycredit
